    • Method Detail

      • checkin

        public Optional<ParkingSlot> checkin​(Car car)
        Allows to checkin a car in the parking. It reserves a parking slot and sets the arrival time. If no parking slot is available for the right type, the checkin is refused, no parking slot will be returned. This operation is thread safe.
        Parameters:
        car - a car
        Returns:
        a parking slot utilization if available
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the car is null

      • checkout

        public Optional<ParkingTime> checkout​(ParkingSlot parkingSlot)
        Allows to checkout a car from the parking. The parking slot is freed and becomes available for checkin. The departure time is set when the car is leaving. This operation is thread safe.
        Parameters:
        parkingSlot - the parking slot to be freed
        Returns:
        a parking slot utilization
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if parking slot is null
